                    <li><b>South:</b> Central Jail Road</li>
                    <li><b>East:</b> Central Jail Road</li>
                    <li><b>West:</b> Beatson Road</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The complex is nestled in the heart of Bhagalpur, surrounded by the villages of Adampur, Kalibari, and Khunjurpur.</p>
                <h3 class="my-3">Significance</h3>
                <p>Sandy's Compound is not only a hub for sports and recreational activities but also a place that blends natural beauty with modern amenities. It serves as a vital community space in Bhagalpur, offering diverse activities for people of all ages. Whether you're a sports enthusiast, a fitness seeker, or someone looking to relax in a beautiful setting, Sandy's Compound provides the perfect environment.</p>
